Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_partitions(25.10)                              report_partitions(25.10)

Name
       report_partitions  -  Reports  all partitions and clones in a tree like
       format

Syntax
       report_partitions

       [-help]

       Reports all partitions and clones in a tree like format.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes the type  and  default
              information for each report_partitions parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man report_partitions

Example
       The following command prints the partitions and clones in the design in
       a tree like format.

       report_partitions

       Format:  partitionName, MasterOrClone, OrientWrtCell, PartitionOrBlack-
       Box   (CommittedOrUncommited,  Level,  BottomUpLevel,  In/Active):  In-
       stOrHInstName

        - dtmf_recvr_core (design name)

          -  ptn_wrapper(0x7f956bb4c140),  Clone,  MY,  Partition   (Uncommit-
       ted,1,1,Active): PTN_INST2

            - ram_128x16_test(0x7f956bb4c0e0), Clone, MY, Partition    (Uncom-
       mitted,2,0,Active): PTN_INST2/RAM_128x16_TEST_INST2

            -  ram_128x16_test(0x7f956bb4c080),  Clone, R180, Partition   (Un-
       committed,2,0,Active): PTN_INST2/RAM_128x16_TEST_INST1

          - ptn_wrapper(0x7f9551444b18), Master,  R0,  Partition    (Uncommit-
       ted,1,1,Active): PTN_INST1

            -  ram_128x16_test(0x7f956bb4c020), Clone, MX, Partition   (Uncom-
       mitted,2,0,Active): PTN_INST1/RAM_128x16_TEST_INST1

            - ram_128x16_test(0x7f95514443c8), Master, R0, Partition   (Uncom-
       mitted,2,0,Active): PTN_INST1/RAM_128x16_TEST_INST2

          -  tdsp_core(0x7f9551444770),  Single,  R0,  Partition    (Uncommit-
       ted,1,0,Active): TDSP_CORE_INST

